Product Name: Section connector, gap filler & hardware for 1" gap
Product Description: Section Connector work sheet used for R026,M2000 & M2400
Spec 2: SECTION #1 (PER GAP, PER TIER, 2ND TIER AND UP)
Spec 3: Using the work sheet 1) Determine the gap between the sections (the best way is to measure the top deck) 2) Find the gap size that you have in Section #1. 3) One per gap, one per tier, 2nd tier and up. 4) Add the number in the Qty. column and times by the price, for the total 5) Section #2 is for 1st tier only. Find the same gap. 6) Add the number in the Qty. column and times by the price, for the total. Installation note:       1) Section connectors are required only if the sections are manual 2) Sections can be moved together or a tube added to fill the gap. 3) Section connectors must be installed over the deck supports.
